Ray  origin(0,0), direction ( 1,1)
================
Box( center (3,2), sides (2,2) ): first check intersection with a bounding circle - true, make shape-intersection test - true, t = 2
Box( center (6,0), sides (2,2) ): first check intersection with a bounding circle - false, skip shape-intersection test
